Privacy Policy for LightCowcontrol
Effective Date: [06/12/2024]

Thank you for using Cow Controller App (“the App”). Your privacy and the integrity of our intellectual property are critically important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your data, protect our intellectual property, and the consequences of violations. By using the App, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.

1. Data Collection and Usage
We collect minimal personal information necessary for the app’s functionality, including but not limited to user credentials and activity logs. This data is used to improve app performance and ensure security.
Your data will never be sold or shared with third parties without your explicit consent, except as required by law.
2. Intellectual Property Rights
All intellectual property related to the Cow Controller App, including but not limited to the app’s design, source code, and branding, is owned solely by the developer of the app (Lightgroup).

Prohibited Actions:
Claiming Ownership: If any individual or entity falsely claims ownership of the App, they will be liable to pay 1,000,000,000 USD as a penalty.
Duplication or Access to Source Code: Unauthorized duplication, reverse engineering, or access to the source code is strictly prohibited. Violators will be liable to pay 19,999,999 USD as a penalty.
Negative Publicity: Engaging in malicious or intentionally damaging publicity against the App will result in a penalty of 1,000 USD.
3. Security Measures
We employ state-of-the-art security measures to protect user data and our intellectual property. While we strive to provide a secure platform, users are responsible for safeguarding their accounts and must not engage in activities that compromise app security.

4. Limitation of Liability
The app is provided “as-is” without warranties of any kind. We are not liable for any damages arising from the use of the App, except as explicitly stated in this policy.

5. Legal Jurisdiction
This Privacy Policy is governed by the laws of [Cameroon]. Any disputes related to this policy or the App will be resolved exclusively in the courts of [Insert Jurisdiction].

6. Changes to the Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. Users will be notified of significant changes via in-app notifications or email.

